<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zgh" dir="ltr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Igmaḍ n llab ttwakemlen — Terroir.ma</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: 'Tifinagh', 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px;">
  <h1 style="color: {{#if passed}}#2e7d32{{else}}#c62828{{/if}};">
    Igmaḍ n llab — {{#if passed}}Ittawafaqen ✓{{else}}Ur ittawafaqen ✗{{/if}}
  </h1>

  <p>Aselway,</p>

  <p>
    Igmaḍ n llab i yettwaggen ɣef alot-nnek <strong>ttwakemlen</strong>.
    Ɣer da mazalt n tizeɣwa:
  </p>

  <table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 24px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background: #f5f5f5; font-weight: bold;">Asmil n alot</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">{{batchReference}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background: #f5f5f5; font-weight: bold;">Amekli</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">{{productName}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background: #f5f5f5; font-weight: bold;">Tizeɣwa</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; color: {{#if passed}}#2e7d32{{else}}#c62828{{/if}}; font-weight: bold;">
        {{#if passed}}Yettawafaq i yilugan SDOQ{{else}}Ur yettawafaq ara — asentem yettwekkes{{/if}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background: #f5f5f5; font-weight: bold;">Llab</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">{{labName}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background: #f5f5f5; font-weight: bold;">Azemz n ukmil</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">{{completedAt}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  {{#unless passed}}
  <p style="background: #ffebee; border-left: 4px solid #c62828; padding: 12px; margin: 24px 0;">
    <strong>Asiggel iḥettem:</strong> Alot-nnek ur yessefrak ara i yilugan n SDOQ.
    Bḍu s ujiɣ n usentem i wakken ad teẓreḍ tigawin tiqbilen.
  </p>
  {{/unless}}

  <p style="margin-top: 32px; color: #666; font-size: 0.9em;">
    Iyawalen-a ttwaznen s wudem awurman seg usebter Terroir.ma.<br>
    Ur d-trarreḍ ɣef yiyawalen-a.
  </p>
</body>
</html>
